cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SY

The paper discusses the use of Federated Learning (FL) in mobile edge networks, which involves both machine learning and networking concepts. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses resource allocation and optimization, which falls under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
